sub.CreateBBSAll: $id = 1 while $id < 70 gosub sub.CreateBBSParsed inc $id = end endsub
sub.CreateBBSParsed: if read text: page id=$page, id=$id exists $article.text = sprintf: fmt='%s.%s', $article, $id, null, null, null $table = table alloc $tArticles[$article.text] = $table $table['is.dynamic'] = [FALSE] $table['article'] = $article.text $table['id'] = $id $table['page.id'] = $page if $race $table[$race] = $race end
$value = 10000 + $id if read text: page id=$page, id=$value exists $table['tab'] = $value else $read.text = read text: page=$page id=$id $idx = find position of pattern '[title]' in $read.text if $idx != -1 $idx = $idx + 7 $endIdx = find position of pattern '[/title]' in $read.text if $endIdx != -1 if $endIdx > $idx $len = $endIdx - $idx $read.text = get substring of $read.text offset=$idx length=$len $table['tab'] = $read.text end end end end end endsub
sub.CreateBBS: $article.text = sprintf: fmt='%s.%s', $article, $id, null, null, null $table = table alloc $tArticles[$article.text] = $table $table['is.dynamic'] = [FALSE] $table['article'] = $article.text $table['id'] = $id $value = $id + 1 $table['author'] = $value $value = $id + 2 $table['tab'] = $value $value = $id + 3 $table['title'] = $value $table['page.id'] = $page endsub
sub.CreateSalesArray: $array.sales = $table.hq['sales'] if not $array.sales $array.sales = array alloc: size=11 $i = size of array $array.sales while $i dec $i = $t = table alloc $array.sales[$i] = $t end $table.hq['sales'] = $array.sales end endsub
sub.CreateHQ: $table.hq = $table['hq'] if not $table.hq $table.hq = table alloc $table['hq'] = $table.hq $table.hq['respawn'] = [TRUE] $table.hq['destroyed'] = -1 gosub sub.CreateSalesArray $array.sales[0][Singularity Engine Time Accelerator] = [TRUE] $array.sales[0][Engine Tuning] = [TRUE] $array.sales[0][Rudder Optimisation] = [TRUE] $array.sales[0][Cargo Bay Extension] = [TRUE] else $array.sales = $table.hq['sales'] end endsub
sub.CreateShipyard: $table.hq = $table['shipyard'] if not $table.hq $table.hq = table alloc $table['shipyard'] = $table.hq $table.hq['respawn'] = [TRUE] $table.hq['destroyed'] = -1 gosub sub.CreateSalesArray else $array.sales = $table.hq['sales'] end endsub
sub.CreateGuildData: $table = $data[$guild.name] if not $table $table = table alloc $table['member'] = [FALSE] $table['level'] = 0 $table['exp'] = 0 $table['agent'] = 111 $table['id'] = 0 $array.ranks = array alloc: size=11 $table['ranks'] = $array.ranks $array.ranks[0] = 322 $array.ranks[1] = 19001 $array.ranks[2] = 19002 $array.ranks[3] = 19003 $array.ranks[4] = 19004 $array.ranks[5] = 19005 $array.ranks[6] = 19006 $array.ranks[7] = 19007 $array.ranks[8] = 19008 $array.ranks[9] = 19009 $array.ranks[10] = 19010 $table['nameid'] = $guild.name
$data[$guild.name] = $table else $array.ranks = $table['ranks'] end endsub
